## 10. Configuracion avanzada

### `opencode.json` — Configuracion del plugin

Seccion `apolo-dynamic-flow.config`:

```json
{
  "apolo-dynamic-flow": {
    "config": {
      "circuit_breaker_policy": "fail-closed",
      "max_loops_per_phase": {
        "reanclaje": 2,
        "verdad": 2,
        "plan-indice": 2,
        "implementation": 4
      },
      "evidence_collection": {
        "auto_recollect_on_stale": true,
        "stale_check_interval_seconds": 300
      },
      "tests": {
        "auto_run_on_micro_change": true,
        "auto_rollback_on_fail": true,
        "rollback_strategy": "git-restore"
      },
      "telemetry": {
        "enabled": true,
        "panel_port": 8080
      },
      "tools": {
        "absorb_on_session_start": true,
        "health_check_interval_seconds": 300
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### `routing-rules.json` — Routing declarativo

10 reglas editables sin recompilar TypeScript:

```json
[
  {
    "id": "R-001",
    "trigger": "evidence-insufficient",
    "action": "recollect-with-agent",
    "description": "Si score_evidence < 0.4, pedir al agente mas evidencia"
  },
  {
    "id": "R-002",
    "trigger": "plan-too-large",
    "action": "split-plan",
    "description": "Si plan tiene > 5 unidades, partir en subplanes"
  }
]
```

### `security_config.yaml` — Allowlist + SSRF

```yaml
allowlist:
  origins:
    - "github://juancspjr/*"      # GitHub del autor
    - "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/*"
    - "https://opencode.ai/*"
  denylist:
    - "http://169.254.169.254/*"  # AWS metadata
    - "http://localhost:*"        # SSRF
    - "http://127.0.0.1:*"
    - "https://evil.com/*"

ssrf_protection:
  enabled: true
  block_private_ips: true
  block_localhost: true
  block_metadata_endpoints: true
```

### `.opencode/apolo-dynamic/apolo-auto-hooks.yaml` (v2.9.0)

Configuracion de auto-hooks (9 triggers):

```yaml
autohooks: V1
version: 1
enabled: true
triggers:
  - name: phase-complete:init
    enabled: true
    run:
      - script: health_check.py
        args: ["--repo-root", "."]
        timeout: 30
    condition: null
    description: "Despues de init, ejecutar health check"

  - name: phase-complete:verdad
    enabled: true
    run:
      - script: code_quality.py
        args: ["--repo-root", "."]
        timeout: 120
      - script: vulnerability_scanner.py
        args: ["--repo-root", "."]
        timeout: 120
    condition: null
    description: "Despues de fase verdad, calidad + vulnerabilidades"

  - name: evidence:collected
    enabled: true
    run:
      - script: secret_scanner.py
        args: ["--scan-stdin"]
        stdin_from: evidence_files
        timeout: 30
    condition: "items >= 1"
    description: "Despues de recolectar evidencia, escanear secretos"
  # ... 6 triggers mas
```

### `.opencode/apolo-dynamic/apolo-post-script-gates.yaml` (v2.9.0)

Configuracion de gates post-script (11 gates):

```yaml
postscriptgates: V1
version: 1
enabled: true
gates:
  - script: collect_evidence.py
    enabled: true
    require:
      - path: items
        type: list
        min_length: 1
        description: "Al menos 1 item de evidencia"
      - path: hash_chain
        type: string
        min_length: 64
        description: "SHA-256 hash chain"
    on_fail: block
    description: "Evidence pack debe tener items + hash chain"

  - script: generate_plan.py
    enabled: true
    require:
      - path: unidades
        type: list
        min_length: 1
      - path: topological_sort
        type: list
    on_fail: block
    description: "Plan debe tener unidades + orden topologico"

  - script: full_audit.py
    enabled: true
    require:
      - path: summary.final_score
        type: number
        min: 0
        max: 100
      - path: summary.grade
        type: string
        min_length: 1
    on_fail: warn
    description: "Full audit debe producir score + grade"
  # ... 8 gates mas
```

